This is a program to convert text to morsecode (written/sound),
morsecode to text (written/sound).

To use it you must have python 3 and pygame for sound playback.

Usage:
Text to written morsecode
python3 morse.py <text here>

Written morsecode to text
python3 morse.py -m "<morsecode here>"

Text to morsecode (sound)
python3 morse.py -p <text here>

Sound to text
python3 morse.py -d <wavsoundfile>

Note that it probably only can decode morse created with this program.
